  "text": "Another issue related to UAVs' data link is with regards to their integration in the NAS. The performance differences between the UAS communication and other traffic types must be considered. This includes the differences in speed, range, and other flight aspects which complicate the ATC responsibilities to manage the co-existence of the manned and unmanned aircraft [CITATION_1] . Hence, for ATC safety analysis, a calculated balance is needed for an unmanned aircraft. compared to the manned aircraft.",
